parameters: Zaidar-Grunt: "Lord Garves, I have a report!"
Zaidar-Grunt: "Spider-Gr has been defeated by Pony-Ceres..."
Warlord Garves: "Spider-Gr has been defeated, you say!?"
Zaidar-Grunt: "Yes..."

Zaidar-Grunt: "The humans we had captured have also been freed by
Pony-Ceres"
Warlord Garves: "..."
Warlord Garves: "...Why are you here?"
Zaidar-Grunt: "...Eh?"

Warlord Garves: "Your being alive and here means you abandoned your
mission to capture the humans and fled back here... Am I wrong?"
Zaidar-Grunt: "...Th-that is"

Warlord Garves: "Trash that forgets their loyalty to Lord Dargnoa has
no value in living"
Zaidar-Grunt: "...Wai-wait a-"
Warlord Garves: "Damn it, Pony-Ceres!!"
Warlord Garves: "If only... If only my power would return...!!"
Sage Domdora: "You seem quite enraged, Lord Garves"
Warlord Garves: "Domdora... What are you doing in a place like this?"

Sage Domdora: "I've heard through the grapevine that you encountered
Pony-Ceres and yet failed to finish them off on the spot"
Sage Domdora: "That won't do... That really won't do"

Sage Domdora: "Did you figure they wouldn't be an obstacle if left
alone, or perhaps... you got cold feet in front of Pony-Ceres...?"
Warlord Garves: "..."

Sage Domdora: "Do you think I don't know? That you fled from that
woman in the battle a hundred years ago"
Warlord Garves: "..."

Sage Domdora: "Either way, letting an enemy who could threaten Lord
Dargnoa escape..."

Sage Domdora: "That would make you incompetent as a Zaidar executive,
wouldn't it?"
Warlord Garves: "...You've come to mock my failure, is that it?"

Sage Domdora: "That's part of it, but I thought I should report to you
as well"

Sage Domdora: "Thanks to my wisdom, the demonic beast weapon,
\C[17]Zaiborg\c[0], has been revived"
Warlord Garves: "That's... a beast that devours humans!"

Warlord Garves: "If such creatures are released on the surface, the
very nation Lord Dargnoa rules will be doomed!"

Sage Domdora: "Rest assured. They will only be released on the surface
in case of an emergency. That is, if your army is defeated by Pony-
Ceres"

Sage Domdora: "Until then, I will take responsibility and keep them
tame underground"
Warlord Garves: "Is Lord Dargnoa aware of this?"

Sage Domdora: "Of course. He highly praised the achievement of
reviving Zaiborg"
Warlord Garves: "Grrr..."

Warlord Garves: "My army being defeated is as unlikely as heaven and
earth flipping over. I will surely present this country and the humans
to Lord Dargnoa!"
Sage Domdora: "Of course. I am looking forward to it as well"

Sage Domdora: "The complete revival of Lord Dargnoa is imminent after
all"
Sage Domdora: "Now if you'll excuse me, Lord Garves. Foh foh foh foh!"
Warlord Garves (Domdora...)
Warlord Garves (To revive Zaiborg... What is he thinking...)
Warlord Garves (Could it be Lord Dargnoa...)
Warlord Garves (...It seems necessary to assign a watch)
